{"tid":1809044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實可唔可以叫「香港人，戰鬥！」","createTime":"2020-01-02T20:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T19:33:22.000Z","uid":195252,"like":42,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"07d482ebefefde40d28bf1ab54a423e207cf4665","tid":1809044,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:18:42.000Z","msg":"見到隔離post講緊唔應該叫「香港人報仇」，因為內容空泛，根本有排都報唔到仇。我諗大部份人都好認同呢一點。<br />\n<br />\n但係又有人覺得叫返「香港人加油」，而我就覺得既然大家心態已經放開左，不如就叫「香港人戰鬥」，因為唔單止勇武戰線，和理非戰線例如成立工會，和你shop，文宣等等活動，都需要大家無比ge決心繼續奮鬥，跟港共，中共政權決一勝負。<br />\n<br />\n咁不如就叫「香港人，戰鬥！」，喻意為戰鬥到底，只許成功。"},{"pid":"06389a3f8eb33b5536e0791e07fd9ba400d51e12","tid":1809044,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:21:46.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"0bec14d7e9ef02b423547338284b33d3b104155c","tid":1809044,"uid":3705,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:22:59.000Z","msg":"如果再淨係得個叫字嘅話<br />\n其實叫乜都冇用"},{"pid":"15d6b121d9db8d76fa8192d86168ff0652520347","tid":1809044,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:24:14.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"77e9d2ac322990a46252a7b603b731e44d5e3414","tid":1809044,"uid":231522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0bec14d7e9ef02b423547338284b33d3b104155c","tid":1809044,"uid":3705,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:22:59.000Z","msg":"如果再淨係得個叫字嘅話<br />\n其實叫乜都冇用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:24:55.000Z","msg":"Sad but true"},{"pid":"122d14f9c5013daa827cef26a39af025be91ffd4","tid":1809044,"uid":70487,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:25:07.000Z","msg":"香港人，獨立！"},{"pid":"ac3ee8a64ef6d3648a0bdfc767aa1e49bd950f1e","tid":1809044,"uid":82917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"122d14f9c5013daa827cef26a39af025be91ffd4","tid":1809044,"uid":70487,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:25:07.000Z","msg":"香港人，獨立！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:25:31.000Z","msg":"叫呢個啦"},{"pid":"49682d7bf5766ae89b5bb89b28dd7c6afb11cb02","tid":1809044,"uid":63639,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:26:32.000Z","msg":"我從來唔叫執仇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得好尷尬<br />\n<br />\n尤其係成班人一見到曱甴就唔行"},{"pid":"882862eb31dfedff6f61db2ac0589acee596e4d7","tid":1809044,"uid":201110,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:27:03.000Z","msg":"無人願意做嘅，我比你七百萬人嗌「香港人，打仗」又點話呀。根本只係心態問題，同口號無關。"},{"pid":"32f94deed38c6366def207c791b29ca73fba79f8","tid":1809044,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:27:53.000Z","msg":"今天我們都是陳梓維"},{"pid":"40ed4c2af167811b9ab81ffa57d9595e8e8ac9b7","tid":1809044,"uid":224916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:28:46.000Z","msg":"如果你問我，我係覺得可以叫「香港人，抗爭」，要將抗爭巳經係生活，抗爭要入血，咁先可以長期同中共鬥"},{"pid":"61a7face997399e9d3d9e0cd786da2601c4aaa93","tid":1809044,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:28:59.000Z","msg":"數碼暴龍？"},{"pid":"6783ad673730da85530f4d702154a5ac0750c0ca","tid":1809044,"uid":135891,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"49682d7bf5766ae89b5bb89b28dd7c6afb11cb02","tid":1809044,"uid":63639,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:26:32.000Z","msg":"我從來唔叫執仇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得好尷尬<br />\n<br />\n尤其係成班人一見到曱甴就唔行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T20:31:29.000Z","msg":"我淨係反抗果期會叫<br />\n叫報仇搞到成場革命建基於仇恨之上咁<br />\n明明香港人係受壓迫反抗"},{"pid":"688907f3d6dd3e5c478d56f0c32c489504474c2a","tid":1809044,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":